<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <body style="font-family:sans-serif;max-width:600px;margin:0 auto;padding:2rem;color:#333;">
    <h2>Thanks for reaching out, <%= @submission.name %>!</h2>
    <p>We received your message and will get back to you shortly.</p>
    <blockquote style="border-left:4px solid #e2e8f0;padding:0.5rem 1rem;color:#555;margin:1.5rem 0;">
      <%= @submission.message %>
    </blockquote>
    <p>In the meantime, feel free to reply to this email if you have anything to add.</p>
    <p style="color:#666;font-size:0.875rem;margin-top:2rem;">This is an automated confirmation — a team member will follow up with you soon.</p>
  </body>
</html>
